      • getTweetsFromLocation

        public List<TwitterFeature> getTweetsFromLocation(double latitude,
                                                  double longitude,
                                                  double radius,
                                                  String since,
                                                  String until)
                                           throws TwitterException
        Get the tweets within a radius around a location, using the location given in the users profile, or the geotag when available. Be careful, the API only allows to retrieve 7 days old tweets.
        Parameters:
        latitude -
        longitude -
        radius - in kilometers
        since - the date from which tweets are retrieved (set to null if not applicable)
        until - the date until which tweets are retrieved (set to null if not applicable)
        Returns:
        Throws:
        TwitterException
